{"tid":1214173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[心寒]立法會外女警向民眾展示勝利笑容(有圖)","createTime":"2019-06-13T03:41:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T05:23:31.000Z","uid":152930,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9ff2e9665f670b5e4ace8e9bfc25b44e029c72ec","tid":1214173,"uid":152930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:41:32.000Z","msg":"今日同其他示威者喺立法會門外清理12號遺下嘅垃圾，期間不斷有軍裝警員巡邏。<br />\n唔少警員喺搜查示威者物資嘅時候不斷冷笑。<br />\n冷笑都算，警員穿過民眾時，民眾高呼:「琴日你哋打完人唔係笑得好開心㗎咩？笑得開心d啦！」<br />\n然後圖中嘅女警故意停下腳步向旁邊嘅民眾展示勝利的笑容。<br />\n可惜我影唔到佢笑果一刻，只係可以跟住佢尾搵機會影張清楚嘅相。<br />\n希望各位巴打絲打可以幫手起佢底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vf8qstZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvf8qstZ.png&h=cdc6cf33&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mrih22E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMrih22E.png&h=5698a59f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a894c216237fb94acbe8bea93242ca0d39db57e4","tid":1214173,"uid":70403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:42:22.000Z","msg":"雞？俾班警犬平時出火？"},{"pid":"4adfdb1633ffd79705cf14e6b0ea334dff59f9c8","tid":1214173,"uid":152930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:43:47.000Z","msg":"我真係好撚嬲，點解可以呢個態度？"},{"pid":"ea87e5ddc9ce62b789c1f0dd3c245fd1ed2393ff","tid":1214173,"uid":152930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:43:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7e3f90c6aca423eeaebf8f71a974ee0ac81bb3f2","tid":1214173,"uid":148361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:55:36.000Z","msg":"一睇就知係臭雞啦"},{"pid":"13b01b99acef813000cb8a0e6cdd2facf2b208fa","tid":1214173,"uid":76745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:56:22.000Z","msg":"軍妓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"436e0b6a7a57d22a5f5734c4b8a0836feef51912","tid":1214173,"uid":51768,"like":0,"dislike":0,